Project :- A Premium Bag Shop


Day 23 :-> Backend Project 1 Part-1 | Scatch - A Premium Bag Shop 


Day 24 :-> Backend Project 1 Part-2 | Scatch | Modeling the Database


Day 25 :-> Backend Project 1 Part-3 | Scatch | Separation of Concerns


Day 26 :-> Backend Project 1 Part-4 | Scatch | Development/Production Setup



installation :- 
                npm inti -y
                npm i express
                npm i ejs
                npm i mongoose
                npm i cookie-parser
                npm i jsonwebtoken
                npm i bcrypt
                npm i multer
                npm i debug

                set DEBUG=development:*
                set DEBUG=

                npm i config

                set NODE_ENV=development









Frontend :-
            user Model :- (User Details)

            full Name - string
            email - string
            password  - string
            cart - array
            isAdmin - boolean
            orders - array
            contact - number
            picture - database



            product :- (Product Details)
            
            image
            name
            price
            discount
            bgColor
            panelColor
            textColor









/ -> signup or login
/shop -> shop
/users/cart -> cart
/admin -> admin panel
/owner/products -> show all products
/owner/admin -> show admin panel to create products        
